{"tid":1059813,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[考古]一人一個上個年代嘅創作","createTime":"2019-03-13T11:08:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-13T22:36:05.000Z","uid":225916,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"738379e93dd3eadd29a22129898c04b68e338d02","tid":1059813,"uid":225916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T11:08:58.000Z","msg":"大概早10年前嗰時真係好多有趣嘅野<br />\n拋下磚先<br />\n<br />\n網絡歌手<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/rA1YAx5ByLI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FrA1YAx5ByLI&d=WTugOjWmLb2R3dS25JBA%2BUPclXdXKQfB%2FlJdEd6ZkMI%3D&h=a1b342bd\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/rA1YAx5ByLI</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/TyQlwZ5vYkg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FTyQlwZ5vYkg&d=WTugOjWmLb2R3dS25JBA%2BUPclXdXKQfB%2FlJdEd6ZkMI%3D&h=15154279\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/TyQlwZ5vYkg</a><br />\n(嗰2張相好似同佢本人冇關係，盡興唔係Stephen 唱 啲人覺得把聲似 傳傳下就以為係佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n改對白<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/sU5b67UAQXw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FsU5b67UAQXw&d=WTugOjWmLb2R3dS25JBA%2BUPclXdXKQfB%2FlJdEd6ZkMI%3D&h=80a40513\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/sU5b67UAQXw</a><br />\n<br />\n仲有好多<br />\n阿婆的故事,沙田閪王 哩啲創作已經變成經典<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講少少自己嘅感受<br />\n由幾時開始本土已經再冇咩創作，變成文化沙漠<br />\n<br />\n今時今日係人都可以係youtuber<br />\n拍嘅野都開始一色一樣<br />\n人人都抄襲其他人嘅野變成自己嘅野<br />\n目的係為左搵錢 賣廣告 諗住做網紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以前啲人改歌改詞<br />\n唔係為左搵錢 根本冇錢收<br />\n而係將佢當做興趣 本質上差咗好遠<br />\n質素都愈嚟愈低<br />\n<br />\n到觀眾方面<br />\n因為太多youtuber<br />\n太多資訊 大家接收唔到咁多嘅時候就變成篩選<br />\n久而久之 對於創作嘅水準要求愈嚟愈高<br />\n大家都開始冇勇氣行出身一步去創作<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家有咩上個時代嘅本土創作<br />\n不妨分享一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n等睇俾人話老嘢"},{"pid":"a88ef8cea663e3d184cdc2cb635a266f730850fc","tid":1059813,"uid":225916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T11:11:37.000Z","msg":"好多網絡歌手唱歌都唔錯 去youtube都搵到一大堆其實都好正"},{"pid":"531b3e5904f002a2cc7c4fd4624ffee12690e4ed","tid":1059813,"uid":206623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T11:13:56.000Z","msg":"我覺得係近幾年啲人怕左出名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />怕比人笑<br />\n冇左個人主義<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cf11c2c4404bf32a72dd5b620ac6a7944abee8e","tid":1059813,"uid":225916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"531b3e5904f002a2cc7c4fd4624ffee12690e4ed","tid":1059813,"uid":206623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T11:13:56.000Z","msg":"我覺得係近幾年啲人怕左出名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />怕比人笑<br />\n冇左個人主義<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T11:16:33.000Z","msg":"係 <br />\n喺一個群體社會下<br />\n大家都想需要人認同，會好在意其他人想法<br />\n如果唔合群，唔去跟隨著批評人<br />\n可能就會被人恥笑<br />\n冇咗獨立意識"},{"pid":"fbb3a575cbef1536fc047a01edc6c232af1cfce0","tid":1059813,"uid":225916,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T11:18:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/grBLUgk65pE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FgrBLUgk65pE&d=WTugOjWmLb2R3dS25JBA%2BUPclXdXKQfB%2FlJdEd6ZkMI%3D&h=dafbe726\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/grBLUgk65pE</a>"},{"pid":"0c1bd7f84970e15500ec19050c2f5be0cbf41d5b","tid":1059813,"uid":225916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T11:29:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"861325a298509aa09d487763e358d214eb72d5cd","tid":1059813,"uid